                  <summary>Authorization addressed to the sitologi of the middle toparchy Kerkeuron kai Petne topon by Alexandrus for the payment of 20 artabae to Theon. (Grenfell &amp; Hunt)</summary>
                  <msItem>
                     <note type="general">Text is on one side only, 12 lines written with the fibers.  All margins are visible.</note>
                     <textLang mainLang="grc">Greek</textLang>
                  </msItem>
               </msContents>
               <physDesc>
                  <p>5.7 X 11.8cm. Torn on the bottom left, large tears in the center.  The top left corner has been repaired with tape, which obscures the first word of the first line and makes it difficult to read.</p>
